# React Native New Architecture

Always set `RCT_NEW_ARCH_ENABLED=1` when running iOS/Android builds or e2e tests. Never run without New Architecture enabled.

- Build: `RCT_NEW_ARCH_ENABLED=1 detox build ...`
- Test: `RCT_NEW_ARCH_ENABLED=1 detox test ...`
- Pod install: `RCT_NEW_ARCH_ENABLED=1 pod install`
